Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been an eventful journey for Polestar so far and not without obstacles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这对Polestar来说是一次坎坷但不平凡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but through determination, innovation and an obsession with detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,仰仗我们的决心、创新和对细节的执着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally arrived at a very exciting stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们终于达到了一个激动人心的阶段：
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,VP, verification prototype build.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,验证原型制造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one thing to design a car that challenges existing norms,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,它是汽车设计中一项挑战常规的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,while also raising the bar for electric cars the world over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,同时也将电动汽车提升至世界级水准
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another thing entirely to realize that design in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然而将这种设计变为现实又是另一回事。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From aesthetics to driver experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,从美学到驾驶体验
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,no stone is left unturned during these builds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不遗余力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The VP cars are the first build series and a major player in these prototype builds is carbon fiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,原型车是首个生产系列，而构建它们的主角就是碳纤维
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Carbon fiber figures hugely in the Polestar1.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,碳纤维是Polestar1极其重要的组成部分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,ten times stronger and five times lighter than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,比钢材强度高10倍，而重量却只有五分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Carbon fiber is the ideal material to realize the ambitious plans for this car
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,碳纤维是实现这个宏大计划的理想材料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the body more rigid and therefore create more responsive handling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它使车身更坚固，因此带来了更敏捷的操控性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire upper body of the Polestar1 is carbon fiber reinforced polymer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Polestar1整个车身上部是碳纤维增强聚合物(CFRP)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the true carbon fiber game changer is the dragonfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的碳纤维变革者是"蜻蜓"结构
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A CFRP patch bonded to the steel underbody to increase torsional stiffness by 45%.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,CFRP补片粘接到钢车身底板上，增加45%的抗扭刚度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragonfly, actually three parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"蜻蜓"结构实际上分为三部分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the body and the wings glued into place and fired in the oven at 85 degrees for 45 minutes also strengthens this traditionally weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,主体和翼片被粘接并放入烤箱，在85度下烘烤45分钟以加固原先的薄弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The next stop is the hang on parts area,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,下一站是零件装夹处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:02:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,where components are measured with unforgiving precision before they're attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:02:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,总装前，零件将会在此以严苛的标准监测。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The slightest of misalignments can cause a disruption of the feature lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,即使最轻微的错位也会造成特征线的中断
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,thus compromising the Polestar1's distinctive design.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,从而破坏Polestar1的独特设计
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Working with carbon fiber, however, can present different challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,处理碳纤维有很多难点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,painting, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,以喷涂工艺为例
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,carbon fiber substrates aren't smooth and free of imperfections like steel,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,碳纤维基材表面并不光滑，不像钢材那样完美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and they have a distinctive weave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,并且有独特的编织纹理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The solution,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,解决办法是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,a combination of machine sanding and hand sanding to give the panels a smooth, even finish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一系列的机器和手工打磨加工出组件的光滑表面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,fine sanding is done by hand to ensure the integrity of the feature lines and to stay true to the initial design.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,精磨由手工完成，确保特征线与初始设计一致
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The marriage point is the true test of all this exacting measurement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,组装点是对之前严格测量结果的一次真正测试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the chassis is attached to the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这个阶段，底盘将和车身合装(marriage)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The parts are attached by a series of bolts protruding from the chassis,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,它们之间由一系列底盘突出的螺栓固定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which then slide into the upper body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这些螺栓之后会插入车身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If even one of the bolts is misaligned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,即使有一个螺栓没有校准
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the process must begin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,整个过程都要推倒重来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,With every Union performed, the process goes more smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,得益于每个团体的出色工作，生产进程也更加顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This means fewer adjustments and a shorter construction time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着更少的调整耗时和更短的生产时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,closer and closer to perfection with each marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,也使得每次合装都更加臻于完美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,双语字幕：@PolestarX
